            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間23日09:26，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲978.7點（或2.58%），暫報38857.17點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 週：+3.15%</li><li>近 1 月：+12.92%</li><li>近 3 月：+19.32%</li><li>近 6 月：+37%</li><li>今年以來：+30.78%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>焦點個股</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>赴美設廠概念領漲+2.58%。其中    臻鼎-KY(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:4958:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/4958\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">4958-TW</a>)            上漲        10%            ;        可成(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2474:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2474\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2474-TW</a>)            上漲        9.74%            ;        台積電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)            上漲        3.41%    。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>18吋晶圓概念領漲+1.69%。其中    辛耘(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:3583:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/3583\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">3583-TW</a>)            上漲        9.92%            ;        台積電(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:2330:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/2330\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">2330-TW</a>)            上漲        3.41%            ;        中砂(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:1560:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/1560\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">1560-TW</a>)            上漲        2.24%    。</p></section></main>",
